FBIS4-60140 "drnes099_n_94005" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 21 May 1994 LEBANON Reaction to al-Dirani Seizure Reported Reaction to al-Dirani Seizure Reported Al-Musawi: `Bargaining' Ploy Doomed NC2105092294 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0900 GMT 21 May 94 NC2105092294 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] In a statement to REUTER today, Husayn al-Musawi, a Hizballah leader, confirmed the report on the abduction of al-Haj Mustafa al-Dirani. He said that this Israeli operation is part of the ongoing fighting between Hizballah and Israel. Al-Musawi added that Israel wants to use al-Dirani as a bargaining chip to insure the release of navigator Ron Arad. But this Israeli attempt will not succeed, he added.
